Well, I've tested using my own machine. Actually, there was a peak when a certain test was executed. I guess it's test_batch_sampler. Except this, the others are fine.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9998726/38093214-dbc3abe6-339c-11e8-8950-16d8d715d8b3.png)
But when I run this test one more time, the peak is gone. That's so weird.
